{"tid":2261061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台海緊張升高 台灣擴大「戰備周」 全國兵力大演練","createTime":"2020-10-28T05:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T11:11:54.000Z","uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62e6b881fb4296218c5091bf95a492f81745b2fd","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:02:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">33化兵群戰力防護 強化全天候作戰效能</span></strong><br />\n民國109年10月27日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/3f035bf7-2a7c-4e84-a4c9-ad57e7aab070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F3f035bf7-2a7c-4e84-a4c9-ad57e7aab070.jpg&h=f2379443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n33化兵群「戰備任務訓練實兵操演」。（軍聞社記者謝宏檜攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/52b12153-5668-4c03-b3de-2b7771f9cb54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F52b12153-5668-4c03-b3de-2b7771f9cb54.jpg&h=fc3076b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n33化兵群「戰備任務訓練實兵操演」。（軍聞社記者謝宏檜攝）<br />\n<br />\n（軍聞社記者謝宏檜桃園27日電）陸軍第六軍團33化學兵群今日執行第四季「戰備任務訓練實兵演練」，派遣偵二連官兵前往戰術位置實施戰力防護，以模擬戰時想定強化官兵臨戰作為，進而提升作戰效能。<br />\n<br />\n 凌晨三點天色未亮，偵消營官兵即全副武裝展開操演任務，由33化學兵群派遣重型消毒車、核生化偵檢車及戰術輪車等裝備，機動至戰術位置實施輜重開設及相關戰備整備，官兵配合現地設施執行偽裝，完成集結地戰力防護作為，發揮平時訓練成效，更充分展現化兵部隊「平時能救災、戰時能作戰」的堅強能量。<br />\n<br />\n 偵二連連長李上尉表示，此次參與操演的官兵，從現地偵查、兵棋推演、現地戰術至實兵演練，每個人都盡心盡力，戮力完成訓練任務，充分發揮化學兵全天候作戰效能，進而守護國人安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/bcbb800d-4c0a-4a2d-9406-25bd6c085f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2Fbcbb800d-4c0a-4a2d-9406-25bd6c085f0b.jpg&h=b0f8719d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重型消毒車至戰術陣地實施戰力防護。（軍聞社記者謝宏檜攝）重型消毒車至戰術陣地實施戰力防護。（軍聞社記者謝宏檜攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/417649dd-8569-41e5-ac2f-e5d54d029f5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F417649dd-8569-41e5-ac2f-e5d54d029f5a.jpg&h=119ce07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n官兵執行偵檢車偽裝。（軍聞社記者謝宏檜攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=994de0de-2bf3-42b1-8182-cf2ba9b94082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FUserKey%3D994de0de-2bf3-42b1-8182-cf2ba9b94082&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=0399bf68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=994de0de-2bf3-42b1-8182-cf2ba9b94082</a>"},{"pid":"02711bcfad7114c6a2db6b73b683aa358ff6e35e","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">586旅甲車機動訓練 結合全民國防教育</span></strong><br />\n民國109年10月27日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/59e21b6d-6537-40b2-a6c9-6b56eeb4b4ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2F59e21b6d-6537-40b2-a6c9-6b56eeb4b4ee.jpg&h=687cb01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八輪甲車行經過程中，民眾給予高度的評價與肯定。（十軍團提供）<br />\n<br />\n（軍聞社記者陳軍均臺中、南投27日電）陸軍第10軍團副参謀長鐘上校今日至岳崗營區，視導586旅執行國造八輪甲車由兵整中心採自力機動方式返回坪頂營區；藉由長距離的機動訓練，除了實際驗證甲車機動性能外，更同步結合「實兵、實裝、實地、實作」之訓練要求，使甲車駕駛人員熟稔戰場地形環境，充分展現平時勤訓精練成果。<br />\n<br />\n 鐘副參謀長表示，國造新式甲車，具備優異的機動性能與防護力，在道路高速機動、快速打擊等方面，均遠勝國軍現役各型甲車，對於作戰區的聯合作戰效能將有相當大的助益；另外，沿途除了民眾給予高度的評價與肯定外，在經過南投高中時，更感受到青年學子的熱情活力，國軍將持續秉持家園由我守護的理念，堅實部隊戰力，以作為國家最堅强的後盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=cd7ef552-b527-488f-90c7-c32f9ebd51a0#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FUserKey%3Dcd7ef552-b527-488f-90c7-c32f9ebd51a0%23&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2fadfba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=cd7ef552-b527-488f-90c7-c32f9ebd51a0#</a>"},{"pid":"65173d6b32d3024712cd83a3ce8adc0985b015e6","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">火箭營戰力防護演練 提升實戰效能</span></strong><br />\n民國109年10月27日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/Cms_Data/Contents/MNA/Media/images/news/e5589841-8f0b-44d3-aa7b-6f1bfb5565f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2FCms_Data%2FContents%2FMNA%2FMedia%2Fimages%2Fnews%2Fe5589841-8f0b-44d3-aa7b-6f1bfb5565f7.jpg&h=5a849239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陸軍第21砲兵指揮部雷霆2000多管火箭依令實施機動。（軍聞社記者周力行攝）<br />\n<br />\n（軍聞社記者周力行桃園27日電）為訓練各級部隊熟悉作戰任務及戰場環境，陸軍第21砲兵指揮部今日執行第四季「戰備任務訓練實兵演練」，火箭營官兵依令前往戰術位置執行戰力防護，以驗證各階段戰力防護執行成效，提升實戰能力。<br />\n<br />\n 清晨5時天仍未明，營區交管人員已就緒，12輛雷霆2000多管火箭及多輛輕型戰術輪車駛離駐地，依計劃路線機動前往蔽點實施戰力保存，全程採實兵實裝方式進行演練；車輛進入戰術位置後，官兵就地架設偽裝網實施隱蔽，與週遭環境融為一體，有效實施戰力防護作為。<br />\n<br />\n 車長劉上士表示，操演前需針對機動路線與陣地實地進行勘察，同時考量各種交通顧慮，才能在安全前提下實施操演；火箭營官兵經過駐地、基地及戰備訓練實兵操演後，均能結合作戰場景進行各項戰術作為，他們有信心、也有能力守護家園。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=d2602b06-49c5-4f00-b2c0-d69f8cfe2443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmna.gpwb.gov.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FUserKey%3Dd2602b06-49c5-4f00-b2c0-d69f8cfe2443&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=4e443ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mna.gpwb.gov.tw/news/detail/?UserKey=d2602b06-49c5-4f00-b2c0-d69f8cfe2443</a>"},{"pid":"a72330144e6f5d4d8d2a4eecdd2c2b4e5927ac5a","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C2_PG3OGL08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC2_PG3OGL08&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=3bcd2d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C2_PG3OGL08</a><br />\n戰備週操演登場 飛彈車.裝甲部隊全出動"},{"pid":"55330c695606fd4cc41e17dbbaea853750df8999","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ar7g9tSqUNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Far7g9tSqUNs&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2537663b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ar7g9tSqUNs</a><br />\n國軍&quot;戰備周&quot;讓人大開眼界! 雲豹甲車&quot;神偽裝&quot;工程車藏身&quot;回收場&quot;"},{"pid":"8083a8d9e43222c58180df5cd9c3f3d57a2ba0cb","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yVjAP1U5o50\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyVjAP1U5o50&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=93e42f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yVjAP1U5o50</a><br />\n國軍戰備週 海鋒飛彈部隊花蓮演練"},{"pid":"7da857426910c988bc68a48ee34262771b764624","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:16:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_4JixrFeFzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_4JixrFeFzU&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7LP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=a2b50066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_4JixrFeFzU</a><br />\n戰備週操演 阿帕契低空飛越新竹"},{"pid":"29c50bf6ed61f85550f5cdfd27e63e92098454ca","tid":2261061,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/10/26/realtime/8839263.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F10%2F26%2Frealtime%2F8839263.jpg%26x%3D0%26